title: El Kab
description: An Ancient Egyptian site with settlements dating back to prehistoric and Pharaonic times. The site also features rock cut tombs from the 18th Dynasty and two temples primarily in use from the Early Dynastic period to the Ptolemaic period.

properties.description: The ancient settlements and temples surrounded by a fortified wall.
properties.title: Center of Visible Remains of Settlement at El Kab

properties.description: 18th Dynasty tombs linked with the nearby ancient settlement.
properties.title: Center of Visible Remains of Tombs at El Kab
